{"tid":2110311,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"邊隻雲端最好？","createTime":"2020-07-15T23:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T02:50:46.000Z","uid":64099,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d40ecdad7afcc402c66d3a34b53e72aa0f65f275","tid":2110311,"uid":64099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:10:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴打<br />\n想問下有邊隻雲端推介<br />\n<br />\n1. 有流動性文件要經常更改（word,excel etc)<br />\n2. 大量舊相/舊片需要backup到online drive (above 500gb)<br />\n3. 私隱度同安全性想高<br />\n4. 當然價錢都好重要<br />\n<br />\n另外其實我有用開icloud (50gb) for backup record<br />\n咁仲有20幾gb淨，流動文件可以用iCloud<br />\n<br />\n而其他儲存問題可以用其他Online Driver定係統一用icloud 好？<br />\n<br />\n利申：電腦電話iPad耳機手錶=全apple<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f839b6a861aa9723a18faf0eddc2a00c8eff97","tid":2110311,"uid":64099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"3193b2583a3cb226d162c43cd4c30dfe5425278a","tid":2110311,"uid":64099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0704a0e129c815e33c129503ec9750c8fcf5d6ad","tid":2110311,"uid":256957,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/fxj-3zPkmAP8_6egiz4BMqOl-q-qBUkLGB_CRxya36g9cuzQYSYtVA5BEw4twFEU6-7W8IbCvyoxP1R4fPSUlFIzkvXPZ7jsHVZvFc_eHkoUfBVXYSOzemN_zw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2Ffxj-3zPkmAP8_6egiz4BMqOl-q-qBUkLGB_CRxya36g9cuzQYSYtVA5BEw4twFEU6-7W8IbCvyoxP1R4fPSUlFIzkvXPZ7jsHVZvFc_eHkoUfBVXYSOzemN_zw&h=48dff15b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9897eafbbb47e7f88265c4e4e5ebe20909522712","tid":2110311,"uid":178246,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T21:54:07.000Z","msg":